        <!-- Optional: URL for more information about this update -->
        <url>https://github.com/SmartmindTech/SM_Estratoos_plugin/releases/tag/v1.7.22</url>

        <!-- Release notes (keep it brief) -->
        <releasenotes>
            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 1.7.22 - Company-Scoped Instant Messaging</h3>
            <p><strong>New API function for sending messages with company-level tokens</strong></p>

            <h4>New Function:</h4>
            <p><code>local_sm_estratoos_plugin_send_instant_messages</code></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Same API structure as <code>core_message_send_instant_messages</code></li>
                <li>Works with company/category-scoped tokens (IOMAD)</li>
                <li>Recipients must be in the same company as the sender</li>
                <li>Falls back to standard capability check for system tokens</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Key Difference from Core:</h4>
            <p>The core function requires system-level <code>moodle/site:sendmessage</code> capability.
            This plugin function validates at company category level for IOMAD tokens, allowing
            company managers to send messages without site-admin privileges.</p>
            ]]>
        </releasenotes>
